data.title: Beginner: veteran German rappers are back – DW – 09
data.meta_description: The hip-hop trio Beginner from Hamburg made their fans wait 13 years for a new album. The delay may have been Jan Delay, as he pursued a solo career. Now, Beginner have moved on to "Advanced Chemistry".
data.text:
09/03/2016September 3, 2016

The hip-hop trio Beginner from Hamburg made their fans wait 13 years for a new album. The delay may have been Jan Delay, as he pursued a solo career. Now, Beginner have moved on to "Advanced Chemistry".
